divs: Sighting DetailsPossible...Tryed to figure out some other reason for these things being in the picture but could not. We have had a long history of happenings. Call me crazy, but this piture is crazy to. All the pictures is not edited or filtered at 1200dpi scanned on a scanner from a photo that was stored for around 15 years. It is not faked. The first is the whole dark picture. The second is a section just left of my fathers face. The 3rd picture is of a section above that nearing the top of the window cover. If you look closly you will see what I see.
Summary: Brought up the brightness of an old picture and saw this.
